title: Update libpng to v1.6.40 and libexpat to 2.5.0+more
body:
**Description of Change**

This PR updates libpng to v1.6.40 and libexpat to 2.5.0+more.

Updates:
 - expat: 
    - https://chromium.googlesource.com/external/github.com/libexpat/libexpat.git
    - 441f98d02deafd9b090aea568282b28f66a50e36
 - png: 
    - https://skia.googlesource.com/third_party/libpng.git
    - f135775ad4e5d4408d2e12ffcc71bb36e6b48551
